<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_17&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The image displays a small, pixelated, black and white icon set against a solid black background. The icon itself is rendered in shades of white and light gray, creating a stark contrast. It depicts a stylized representation of a recreational vehicle or trailer, resembling a camper van or a caravan. The main body of the vehicle is a horizontal rectangle with softened corners. Within this main body, towards the front, there are two smaller, distinct rectangular shapes, which appear to represent windows. Below the main body, centered, is a small circular or oval shape, likely indicating a wheel or a hitch for the trailer. The overall impression is that of a simple, symbolic graphic."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HOUSE ICON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A very low-resolution, pixelated black and white icon resembling a simple house or building. It features a rectangular base and a triangular or peaked roof, with two small square shapes that could represent windows or doors on its front face. The icon is rendered in white against a black background."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
</node>
